cu.explanation_en: Setting the gNB ID to an invalid hexadecimal value 'invalid_hex' will cause gNB identification failure and prevent proper network initialization.

du.explanation_en: Setting the gNB ID to an invalid hexadecimal value 'invalid_hex' will cause gNB identification failure and prevent proper network initialization.
du.explanation_zh: 將 gNB ID 設定為無效的十六進位值 'invalid_hex' 會導致 gNB 識別失敗，並阻止正確的網路初始化。
